def main():
    """
    Main function
    """
    num_costumes = int(input())
    costumes = []
    for _ in range(num_costumes):
        costumes.append(input())
    costume_set = set(costumes)
    costume_counts = [costumes.count(costume) for costume in costume_set]
    max_count = max(costume_counts)
    winners = [costume for costume, count in zip(costume_set, costume_counts) if count == max_count]
    print('\n'.join(sorted(winners)))

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

from collections import defaultdict

n = int(input())
costumes = [input() for _ in range(n)]

counts = defaultdict(int)
for costume in costumes:
    counts[costume] += 1

max_count = max(counts.values())
best_costumes = [costume for costume, count in counts.items() if count == max_count]
best_costumes.sort()

for costume in best_costumes:
    print(costume)

import sys

N = int(sys.stdin.readline())
costumes = set()
for _ in range(N):
    costumes.add(sys.stdin.readline().strip())

costumes = list(costumes)
costumes.sort()
for costume in costumes:
    print(costume)
